name: Edwards Whittle
description: Hi..I’m Edwards, I’m 49, a single dad of two,I like kids, most especially my little bridget, I’m just a simple guy for all, I don’t like argument, but I love to laugh a lot sorry for give me for that. Yeah, I’m just who I am, I don’t try to be someone else, doing things in my way. Stay cool xx, I like exercising, walking. Lol just like doing nice things. And as for my Match, Im just hoping to see a nice woman out here….that’s just it. About my match lol xx, a special, good looking, caring, loving and understanding woman, just a special one.
